            <title>[FELIX-5968] Posix &apos;ls&apos; command ignores .. unless -a is specified</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5968</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ls command in org.apache.felix.gogo.jline.Posix applies a filter to all paths beginning with a period. .. (parent) begins with a period, but isn&apos;t a hidden directory. .(current) should also be listed without -a.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
